title: Fitbit Flex 2 - The Extra Mile
description: Make life your workout with the all-new Fitbit Flex 2 — a slim, swim-proof fitness wristband that automatically tracks all-day activity, exercise and sleep, with an ultra-slim removable tracker that fits inside bands, bangles, or pendants for a style that’s all your own.
